### **P2.1 Channel Intelligence (all tactics have a channel, but smart joins)**

B2B requirement: “All tactics should have a channel.”  
**What:**

* recommend which tactic channels members should join based on intake \+ behavior  
* detect dead/noisy channels and recommend merge/split

